reviewText: I searched high and low to find this movie and finally I found it. Expensive and short running but it is a movie worth having in your movie vault.  Love Teri Polo, she needs to do more moives like this. She made this movie happen.

reviewText: Danielle Steele creates another heart-warming movie.  The actors were believable and the storyline positive.  A love story with good character development.  A mother-daughter (teenager) movie.
